  const response = await fetch(`${API_URL}/whatsapp/qr/${instanceName}?project_id=${projectId}`, {
    headers: this.getAuthHeader(),
  });
  return handleResponse<{ success: true; qr_code_base64: string; code: string; pairing_code?: string }>(response);
}
```

#### 4. Dashboard UI Component

Create a QR Code Display Component (or add to existing page):
- Poll GET `/api/whatsapp/qr/{instanceName}` every 3 seconds
- Display: `<img src="data:image/png;base64,{base64}">`
- Auto-refresh until status changes to 'connected'
- Show pairing code if available

